<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
   <p>Welcome to The Brewer's Edge, where home brewers and fans of beer come together to share their beer experiences. Sign up only take 10 seconds. Once registered, you can either review an existing home brew or you can become a brewer and post one of your creations from your own home brewery. Then all you have to do is create a batch, and share your beer!</p>

   <p>With a unique number, your fans will be able to review your beer and tell you what they really think!  Cheers, and happy brewing!</p>
   <hr>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6" align="center">

      <body>

        <%= image_tag "tbe.jpg", :height => '57%', :width => '57%' %>
        <h2 align="center">BREW. SHARE. ENJOY!</h2>


      </body>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-6">

    <h2>Log in</h2>

       <%= simple_form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
        <div class="form-inputs">
          <%= f.input :email, required: false, autofocus: true %>
          <%= f.input :password, required: false %>
          <%= f.input :remember_me, as: :boolean if devise_mapping.rememberable? %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions">
          <%= f.button :submit, "Log in" %>
        </div>
       <% end %>

       <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
    </div>
  </div>
<hr>
</div>








